body:
I suspect what happened is that one of the binaries is built with https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/6fa6bd045c98bdc89424a3425e15b5161586a9a7 and the other with https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/3f23f4ddeabbdc0704444d84c158bd6c348a9f10

@av8ramit can correct me if I'm wrong, but I believe we don't currently guarantee that all the nightlies are built from the exact same version (as per https://github.com/tensorflow/community/blob/master/rfcs/20181026-tf-nightly.md)
